<plot>Victor Martin's mission tells a unique adventure. October 1942, Victor Martin is sent in Germany by the Belgian resistance, so he can see with his own eyes where the deportation trains bring the Jews. His mission would lead him to the doors of Auschwitz. The film was made like a historical road-movie, mixing original drawings, archives, and new testimonies.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?311863</url></doc>
